com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.protocol.json

Interface SdkStructuredJsonFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SdkStructuredJsonFactoryImpl

    public interface SdkStructuredJsonFactory
    Common interface for creating generators (writers) and protocol handlers for JSON like protocols. Current implementations include SdkStructuredPlainJsonFactory and SdkStructuredCborFactory
